USER DOCUMENTATION
__________________

This application requires R3.3.2 and runs best in R studio. 

Prior to running ValuesScript, ensure all of the packages listed in the series of library() statements are installed in your R studio browser. 

Ensure you have set your working directory to a folder containing the ValuesScript.R, ui.R and sever.R files, 
With a subfolder titled www which contains the file northSign.png. 

Ensure you have cleared your global environment prior to running any scripts and ensure your machine is connected to the internet.

Video tutorials can be found as YouTube video urls in the shiny application for advice on navigating the application.

